snippet.title: Pac-Man World 2 GBA Walkthrough Part 1-Pac Village
snippet.description:
Here is the start of another walkthrough!

I am doing Pac-Man World 2 for the Game Boy Advance because I have played this game, and I frankly have not found one good walkthrough of this game out there!

So, in this part, we see the opening cutscenes, and do the first level, Pac Village!

By the way, I am not doing commentary for this, since it would just take too long to edit the video, and by that time, the quality would not be too good.
